quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  114,4,"From the evil of the retreating whisperer{1} -",footnotes:1:i.e., a devil who makes evil suggestions to man but disappears when one remembers Allāh.
  114,5,"Who whispers [evil] into the breasts of mankind -"
  114,6,"From among the jinn and mankind",footnotes:1:Evil prompters may be from men as well as from jinn.